\f1\fs26 \ul \uc0\u8232 \ulnone Autonoma ran a 7-step pipeline on OrangeHRM in 10 minutes. The SDK offered PHP (Laravel) \'97 but OrangeHRM uses Symfony. Different ecosystem, same language. I chose TypeScript + Node instead. Three traps I hit along the way: - admin123 works on demo (v5.8) but fails on local (v5.4) \'97 password policy differs - DELETE /endpoint/\{id\} returns 405 \'97 OrangeHRM expects DELETE /endpoint with \{"ids": [id]\} in body - Buzz like endpoint lives under /buzz/shares/ \'97 not /buzz/likes or /buzz/posts/ The fix: a 4-step playbook that turns any PHP/Python/Go/C# app into an Autonoma-compatible target. Here's what I learned about bridging AI testing pipelines with non-Node stacks \uc0\u55357 \u56391  #Autonoma #TestAutomation #Playwright #AIAgents #OrangeHRM , I put Autonoma on a PHP app. I chose a Node.js proxy \'97 here's the 4-step fix and the 3 traps I found., Victor Ematin on LinkedIn \'95 3 min read\u8232 \ul \uc0\u8232 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7470727815475212288?updateEntityUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afs_updateV2%3A%28urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7470727815475212288%2CFEED_DETAIL%2CEMPTY%2CDEFAULT%2Cfalse%29"}}{\fldrslt Autonoma ran a 7-step pipeline on OrangeHRM in 10 minutes. The SDK offered PHP (Laravel) \'97 but OrangeHRM uses Symfony. Different ecosystem, same language. I chose TypeScript + Node instead.\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 \ul Three traps I hit along the way:\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \ul - admin123 works on demo (v5.8) but fails on local (v5.4) \'97 password policy differs\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \ul - DELETE /endpoint/\{id\} returns 405 \'97 OrangeHRM expects DELETE /endpoint with \{"ids": [id]\} in body\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \ul - Buzz like endpoint lives under /buzz/shares/ \'97 not /buzz/likes or /buzz/posts/\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 \ul The fix: a 4-step playbook that turns any PHP/Python/Go/C# app into an Autonoma-compatible target.\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 \ul Here's what I learned about bridging AI testing pipelines with non-Node stacks \uc0\u55357 \u56391 \ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 }}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23autonoma&origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED"}}{\fldrslt 
