s GPU capacity for structured output.\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 \ul Would I use this in production today? Not yet. Would I bet on agent-generated tests for next year's CI? Yes \'97 if the ecosystem keeps maturing \uc0\u55357 \u56520 \ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 \ul What's your experience with AI-generated test code? Works or too fragile?\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 \ul Victor Ematin \'b7 AI Quality Engineering Lead \'b7 $0 budget\ulnone \uc0\u8232 \u8232 }}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/all/?keywords=%23webwright&origin=HASH_TAG_FROM_FEED"}}{\fldrslt 
